  "concentration": false,
  "description": "You touch a willing creature. For the duration, the target's movement is unaffected by &amp;Reference[DifficultTerrain], and spells and other magical effects can neither reduce the target's Speed nor cause the target to have the &amp;Reference[Paralyzed apply=false] or &amp;Reference[Restrained apply=false] conditions. The target also has a Swim Speed equal to its Speed.\n\nIn addition, the target can spend 5 feet of movement to automatically escape from nonmagical restraints, such as manacles or a creature imposing the &amp;Reference[Grappled apply=false] condition on it.\n\nUsing a Higher-Level Spell Slot. You can target one additional creature for each spell slot level above 4.",
